  <scopecontent id="aspace_e6cd15568653955686b37ea1c10b2e7f">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Films, videos, and slides of Cornell University lacrosse games. Also audio tape with a sound bite from Richie Moran. Booklet from the 1976 season filled with clippings about the season's games, Cornell Lacrosse Club Annual Awards Banquet programs. </p><p> Digitization of films can be arranged if requested.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <arrangement id="aspace_c7ee165ccab3a976082fea23f6891ed8">
    <head>COLLECTION ARRANGEMENT</head>
<p>Listed chronologically by date and by opponent's name, when known.</p><p> Some films labeled highlights may refer to a single game.</p>  </arrangement>
